  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642213/RenderMan_Solaris_Pref_Banner..jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433099084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642213/RenderMan_Solaris_Pref_Banner..jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433099084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642225\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Pref_Banner..jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642213\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"894d5a26-931e-4500-a065-c652822738b9\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p><br/></p><p>When rendering it's usually required that you set a default pose or position for your object to become a reference for later renders even if the object deforms or moves around. This is to prevent &quot;swimming&quot; or a texture effect from appearing to slide across the object as it animates. It's typically referred to by its technical name of Pref.<br/><br/><br/></p><p>In Houdini / Solaris, first add a Rest node to set your default pose</p><p>In your Solaris network, add a <em>copyproperty</em> node and set as per the image below.</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642213/RenderMan_Solaris_Pref_12jpg.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433099084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642213/RenderMan_Solaris_Pref_12jpg.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433099084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642228\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Pref_12jpg.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642213\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"39b75915-1a70-4d08-9679-c9e0f78975ff\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/><br/><br/>Add a __Pref AOV from the <em>rendermanrendersettings</em> node under <em>Render Vars (AOVs)</em> → <em>Integrator</em><br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"250\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642213/setAov.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763058495230&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=386&amp;height=250\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642213/setAov.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763058495230&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"662995127\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"setAov.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642213\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"4222481e-b57b-47ee-8086-bca2e4355bad\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642213/setAov.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763058495230&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=772&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642213/setAov.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763058495230&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=386&amp;height=250 1x\"></span><br/><br/><br/></p><p>Fire off a viewport or disk render and in the AOV display, you will now see the _Pref AOV</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642213/RenderMan_Solaris_Pref_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433099330&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642213/RenderMan_Solaris_Pref_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433099330&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642234\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Pref_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642213\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"e0bbb6a6-dfb0-4649-8b9d-f32cda5dd6d3\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p><br/></p><p>From here your renders should use the default position and shape set by the Rest node.</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>"
    }
  },
